  <title><![CDATA[<equation-figure>]]></title>
  <body>
    <p>Use the <![CDATA[<equation-figure>]]> element to represent an equation that functions as form of figure or display. Display equations are intended to be numbered when numbering is desired.
    </p>
    <equation-figure>
      <title>Sample <![CDATA[<equation-figure>]]></title>
